'''6-氯烟碱'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>10</sub>H<sub>13</sub>ClN<sub>2</sub>。它可由[[烟碱|烟碱]]经[[过氧化氢|过氧化氢]]氧化，得N-氧化烟碱，加入[[三氯氧磷|三氯氧磷]]后反应制得，副产物2-氯烟碱可以通过加入[[二异丙胺|二异丙胺]]抑制产生（<1%）。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Synthesis|volume=1998|issue=01|date=1998-01|pages=42–44|doi=10.1055/s-1998-1997|url=http://www.thieme-connect.de/DOI/DOI?10.1055/s-1998-1997|title=6-Pyridylnicotine and Bis-6,6′-nicotine - New Chiral 2,2′-Bipyridines|accessdate=2021-01-15|author=Boris Schmidt, Vera Neitemeier|archive-date=2018-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180607083110/https://www.thieme-connect.de/DOI/DOI?10.1055%2Fs-1998-1997|dead-url=no}}</ref>烟碱在−78 °C和[[正丁基锂|正丁基锂]]反应，再和六氯乙烷反应也可以得到6-氯烟碱。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=PLoS ONE|volume=8|issue=10|language=en|issn=1932-6203|date=2013-10-01|pages=e76557|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0076557|url=https://dx.plos.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0076557|title=Selection of a Novel Anti-Nicotine Vaccine: Influence of Antigen Design on Antibody Function in Mice|accessdate=2021-01-15|author=David C. Pryde, Lyn H. Jones, David P. Gervais, David R. Stead, David C. Blakemore, Matthew D. Selby, Alan D. Brown, Jotham W. Coe, Matthew Badland, David M. Beal, Rebecca Glen, Yvonne Wharton, Gavin J. Miller, Phil White, Ningli Zhang, Michelle Benoit, Karen Robertson, James R. Merson, Heather L. Davis, Michael J. McCluskie|editor=Kim D. Janda|pmid=24098532|pmc=PMC3788104}}</ref>它和[[正丁醇|正丁醇]]在[[碳酸铯|碳酸铯]]和[[催化剂|催化剂]]的存在下于[[甲苯|甲苯]]中反应，可以得到6-丁氧基烟碱。<ref>Ondachi, Pauline Wanjiku (North Carolina State Univ. Raleigh, NC, USA). Synthesis of alkoxy, heterocyclic and fused-​rings derivatives of (S)​-​nicotine from natural nicotine, progress towards the total synthesis of (S)​-​macrostomine. ''Diss. Abstr. Int., B'', 2009 70 (2). DA3345428.</ref>

